INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (240851, 'One of the most challenging aspects for those who are seeking to find the God of their understanding for the first time is His formlessness. It can be difficult to believe in, and connect with, something that cannot be seen. Perhaps this is because although God is in all things He is felt and experienced on levels that relate directly to the condition of our own hearts.', 29323, 0), (240852, 'Working hard is important, but there''s something that matters even more. Believing in yourself. Think of it this way: Every great wizard in history has started out as nothing more than we are now. Students. If they can do it, why not us?', 28, 0), (240853, 'Believe in yourself and have faith in your abilities.', 2878, 0), (240854, 'And that’s basically the end of this story. I know it sounds unbelievable and all. And I’m not saying I can explain all the time travel parts or the magical tattoo parts. You may not even believe me. That’s okay, though. I know it happened and that’s all that counts.', 42293, 0), (240855, 'Believe and faith in God makes all things possible.', 2878, 0), (240856, 'Most Christians believe that Jesus IS God, that Jesus is the same jealous and angry God that abhorred homosexuals and condemned them as "an abomination." He is the same deity that gave instructions on how to beat slaves and the same divine Creator that suggested the stoning of non-believers and disobedient children. You have to accept the good along with the bad... after all, he came not to abolish the Hebrew laws, but to fulfill them (Matthew 5:17).', 4200, 0), (240857, 'If you Believe in yourself, Others will Believe in you,.', 33925, 0), (240858, 'To find yourself different than others, you must believe,behave and act differently.', 4238, 0), (240859, 'Life as time passes may become stale that’s why we have got to believe that the best things are yet to come.', 42294, 0), (240860, 'I don''t beleive in peoples .I don''t think it''s always true.I believe Buddha knowledge and I believe in god ,I beleive in goodness.I think different from others it is the way I am', 42295, 0), (240861, 'Never rule anything out. Even the exact opposite of what you believe.', 160, 0), (240862, 'God''s love and mercy are for all people.', 4239, 0), (240863, 'Doesn´t matter who you are or what you believe. Everybody has a ghost story', 42296, 0), (240864, 'Live life like there''s no tomorrow, and never stop believing in yourself!', 42297, 0), (240865, 'Integrity never goes out of style.', 4239, 0), (240866, 'Crazy is relative.', 42298, 0), (240867, 'A husband and wife honor God when they love and honor each other.', 4239, 0), (240868, 'I know it''s crazy to believe in silly things, but it''s not that easy', 42299, 0), (240869, 'You''re missing the point. It''s not that I believe in what Lee''s saying; it''s that I hope he''s right. I really, really hope he''s right, because what''s the alternative?', 568, 0), (240870, 'I wonder how it is possible to believe in religion and also believe nothing is wrong with you.', 4238, 0), (240871, 'Her eyes Her bodyHer heart Makes me believe In magic In destiny In myself', 38308, 0), (240872, 'We are supposed to be different. Do not try to put round pegs in square holes. When people look at us, believe in yourself.', 5073, 0), (240873, 'Every act and choice you make is creating the real you and shaping your real life.', 4404, 0), (240874, 'Everything that God wants to say to you is recorded in your Bible…straight from His heart to yours.', 4404, 0), (240875, 'When you delight yourself in the Lord, His Word and His ways become the focus and foundation of your life.', 4404, 0), (240876, 'It takes courage to live. It takes even more courage to wonder. But it takes the greatest courage of all to believe.', 19459, 0), (240877, 'An obedient child learns from the example of an obedient parent.', 4239, 0), (240878, 'Only in God can you find true fulfillment.', 4239, 0), (240879, 'The way religion makes thousands believe is itself a miracle.', 4238, 0), (240880, 'Believe. No pessimist ever discovered the secrets of the stars, or sailed to an uncharted island, or opened a new heaven to the human spirit.', 701, 0), (240881, 'Nothing profound ever happens in your life when you remain in your comfort zone.', 26388, 0), (240882, 'It is never too late to show true character.', 26388, 0), (240883, 'If in some radical miracle, the Abrahamic God revealed his existence to the world, I’d accept the belief in the deity — but I still wouldn''t worship it. The jealous and angry God that justified the killings of millions, sent plagues upon first borns, and abhorred homosexuals would not be worthy of my worship.', 4200, 0), (240884, 'It seems the more we know, the less we believe.', 912, 0), (240885, 'There is one possession that can never be taken away as long as you will not allow it to be taken, and that is your word.', 26388, 0), (240886, 'Approach each new day as a new opportunity to be the person you aspire to be.', 26388, 0), (240887, 'If you make anything a higher priority than God, you are worshiping it and not God.', 4239, 0), (240888, 'Believe nothing, no matter who said it, even if I said it, unless it agrees with your own reason and common sense', 42300, 0), (240889, 'I believe that we should all be free to believe what we want and not be condemned for it,” I say without a thought. “I believe in a higher power and that it works within us. Whatever the name doesn''t matter, it''s the thought behind it that matters. It''s the way we live our lives that matter and as long as I believe that there is someone in the sky there to protect us, no one here will ever break me.', 3822, 0), (240890, 'We have the ability to survive anything.', 26388, 0), (240891, 'When you think on the powerful truths of Scripture, God uses His Word to change your way of thinking.', 4404, 0), (240892, 'Everything is possible for one who believes', 33, 0), (240893, 'Do not trust and depend on someone as a godfather but accept God the father of all fathers.', 24873, 0), (240894, 'don''t believe on anything that someone asked you to believe in when in the first place they don''t believe in.', 18539, 0), (240895, 'Never stop believing in your dreams or the power within you to make them come true.', 30218, 0), (240896, 'As you can see marriage is about putting away selfishness and taking on the concept of teamwork.', 4239, 0), (240897, 'Coaching doesn’t start with X’s and O’s. It starts with believing that players win games and coaches win players.', 26388, 0), (240898, 'Transitions themselves are not the issue, but how well you respond to their challenges!', 4239, 0), (240899, 'There are moments in life that one certainly believes he is alive.', 4238, 0), (240900, 'How does it feel to be a part of this beautifully ingenious design. I have faith that there is a chosen moment in which my soul will expand infinitely free from time and space. Some may find that foolish but I have reasons for my beliefs that are uniquely my own. There are hundreds of billions of galaxies making up the universe. Earth is only one planet of billions orbiting inside just one of these 500,000 billion or more galaxies. And I myself am one person. One of over seven billion people living on our dynamic little planet. Instead of being diluted by this infinitesimal proportion I accept it as a challenge and I use science to strengthen my spirituality. It provokes curiosity and redefines my view of logical thinking. I believe that existence is based on the exchange of energy and functionality. Energy is expended to carry out varying tasks ensuring the function of an organism. This is evident in every life form and has been the founding principle supporting lifetimes of discoveries. Energy is spent with purpose. I can''t help but draw the conclusion that the energy required to create the universe itself was done so for a purpose. You and I were created with a purpose. -Tavia Rahki Smith', 42301, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (240901, 'I believe that we are just carriers of God''s wisdom that he uses to refurnish the earth He created. You are carrying part of that wisdom in you. When it''s time to offload it, do so with all passion!', 3301, 0), (240902, 'My first struggle thought me that there is no such thing as luck, but the second made me believe you certainly need it sometimes.', 4238, 0), (240903, 'It’s not how you start that’s important, but how well you finish!', 4239, 0), (240904, 'Believe," said the rumbling voice. "If you are to survive, you must believe.""Believe what?" asked Shadow. "What should I believe?"He stared at Shadow, the buffalo man, and he drew himself up huge, and his eyes filled with fire. He opened his spit-flecked buffalo mouth and it was red inside with the flames that burned inside him, under the earth."Everything," roared the buffalo man.', 14, 0), (240905, 'The key, Gansey found, was that you had to believe that they existed; you had to realized they were part of something bigger. Some secrets only gave themselves up to those who''d proven themselves worthy.', 184, 0), (240906, 'One of the biggest problems with people who think that they are smart is that they believe that the number of times they admit that they are wrong is inversely proportional to theirintellectual level.', 5920, 0), (240907, 'In the midst of all of this perfect beauty, timeless since the days of Eve, it''s the touch of God creating miracles, if in your heart you just believe.', 19349, 0), (240908, 'To abandon all is to take our hearts, place them before the One who created them, and dare to believe He can live life powerfully through our surrendered lives.', 4407, 0), (240909, 'We’d avoid a lot of insecurity, if we fully, wholly believed in God’s wild affection for us.', 4407, 0), (240910, 'i''m not a dreamerI Just believe in Allah (God)', 42302, 0), (240911, 'Success is waking up in the morning and bounding out of bed because there''s something out there that you love to do, that you believe in, that you''re good at - something that''s bigger than you are, and you can hardly wait to get at it again.', 42303, 0), (240912, 'He taught me to fight, to defend myself, to stand up for what I believe in, and protect people I love. I thanked him for that lesson after that weekend in New Orleans when some guy put his hands on Delia, and I had to tear him apart.', 14803, 0), (240913, 'I trutly believe we are a rollercoaster, we are up, down have twist´s, but at the end, you discover you had join it.', 42304, 0), (240914, 'Beware the unbelief of others. It''s contagious!', 4239, 0), (240915, 'Even when the odds are overwhelming, you can believe in God and His promises.', 4239, 0), (240916, 'It is a dangerous trap to believe that our search is over because we have gained all the riches we are going to have.', 24918, 0), (240917, 'When you believe you''ve become the best writer you can be… you still aren’t.', 34470, 0), (240918, 'Unless some people are commissioned for the task, there will be no gospel preachers; unless the gospel is preached, sinners will not hear Christ’s message and voice; unless they hear him, they will not believe the truths of his death and resurrection; unless they believe these truths, they will not call on him; and unless they call on his name, they will not be saved.', 3734, 0), (240919, 'Have confidence in God''s character, love, and power.', 25795, 0), (240920, 'Do you believe that our stories were written from before that we are but actors performing on the stage called life with neither rehearsals nor retakes, the dialogues of our own and a fleeting audience or are you someone who pens down his own story?', 7248, 0), (240921, 'You are my treasure.', 3597, 0), (240922, 'It''s so weird how life is so full of moving around--people coming and going, people passing by each other all day long. You never know which person''s going to steal your heart. You never know which is going to settle your soul. All you can do is look. And hope. And believe.', 18902, 0), (240923, 'The best way to make something last is to believe that it won''t.', 42305, 0), (240924, 'What makes you believe, that you are the only person with so much problems and bad luck? If you wear everyone’s shoes, you will certainly understand that the whole world is drowning in crisis and even you are not among them.', 4238, 0), (240925, 'Elisha,'' he said, ''no matter what happens to me, where I go, what folks say about me, no matter what anybody says, you remember - please remember - I was saved. I was there.', 85, 0), (240926, 'If you don’t do anything today without power', 42306, 0), (240927, 'I don''t know why but they you said it I started believing it.', 42307, 0), (240928, 'Success makes me happy, but it doesn’t give me peace. Because I do believe that success is not enough for our cause. We are born to struggle and nothing must deceive us.', 4238, 0), (240929, 'I did not say it was true, only that I believe it.', 3613, 0), (240930, 'Well," she said, "how can I be sure there aren''t invisible people in the world? Scientists didn''t believe in the mountain gorilla for hundreds of years. And now look. So if scientists can be wrong, then all of us can be wrong. I mean, what if all those invisible people ARE scientists? Think about that one.', 360, 0), (240931, 'I have faith in us as a family, and our friends. I think we will survive because we don’t wish to harm anyone. If you ever need something to believe in, believe that to stand and fight for the people you love is the most honorable thing you can do with your life.', 29618, 0), (240932, 'At this time in his life Zinkoff sees no difference between the stars in the sky and the stars in his mother''s plastic Baggie. He believes that stars fall from the sky sometimes, and that his mother goes around collecting them like acorns. He believes she has to use heavy gloves and dark sunglasses because the fallen stars are so hot and shiny. She puts them in the freezer for forty-five minutes, and when they come out they are flat and silver and sticky on the back and ready for his shirts.', 616, 0), (240933, 'Believe that there are no limits. Manifest your best reality.', 3597, 0), (240934, 'If I don’t believe in your god, it means he was incapable to manipulate me.', 4238, 0), (240935, 'What do you want, Mary Foxe? My husband?" “I believe in him," she said slowly. I wondered if she’d ever told him that, and if so, what he had to say about it. Someone you made up turns around and tells you they believe in you— what response could you possibly make? The scenario is just plain weird. And really kind of impertinent on her part, too. If it happened to me I think I’d be speechless for the rest of my life.', 9941, 0), (240936, 'To be acknowledged that we do not believe in their misleading notion and fallacy, today, tomorrow and forever even if it costs us our life. They have suffocated people for hundreds of years and if we don’t stop them today no one else would do it tomorrow.', 4238, 0), (240937, 'All we have to do is ask and believe that God will work on our behalf and give us what we need to overcome and rise above the adversities and stress that we are facing.', 4250, 0), (240938, 'Pain was as much a part of this life as the summer and the winter and the rain, and there was no greater asshole than the one who believed you can cure it.', 26864, 0), (240939, 'I don''t believe you have to be better than everybody else. I believe you have to be better than you ever thought you could be.', 42308, 0), (240940, 'Well, you ought to stick with it, even after you mess up-but sticking with it is a lot easier if you have a family who believes in you.', 42309, 0), (240941, 'What did you think about?" I wish I could tell him that I thought about him, but I lied to him once and I won''t do it again. And besides, I wasn''t thinking about Xander either. "I thought about angels," I say."Angels?""You know. The ones in the old stories. How they can fly to heaven." "Do you think anyone believes in them anymore?" He asks."I don''t know. No. Do you?""I believe in you," he says, his voice hushed and almost reverent. "That''s more faith than I ever thought I''d have.', 337, 0), (240942, 'I will be merciful, and I will believe in people. If I am to err, I will err on the side of mercy. I will give people the benefit of the doubt. I will bend, but not break, in order to give people the opportunity to grow and develop.', 19085, 0), (240943, 'Tragically, many people have this faithless, wishy-washy mindset, which causes them to lose the battle in their minds before they ever fight it in the world.', 3962, 0), (240944, 'Just because you don''t believe in something doesn''t mean its not real', 42310, 0), (240945, 'When people show you who they are', 42311, 0), (240946, 'The thing is'', (Rufus) Stone said, ''that if you don''t believe that you are an old man, or a woman, or a tramp, then how can you expect anyone else to believe you? Looking the part is just the surface; being the part is the true disguise.', 24753, 0), (240947, 'To live a normal life, you just have to believe nothing is normal.', 4238, 0), (240948, 'Master Chekhov says Man is what he believes. From here we conclude that when Man believes in a crap, Man becomes a crap!', 3701, 0), (240949, 'I still believed he''d love me again somehow, love me that intense, thick way he did, the way that made everything good.', 236, 0), (240950, 'Lie until even you believe it - that''s the real secret of lying', 522, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (240951, 'We each come to create the reality we believe we deserve.', 11173, 0), (240952, 'I want to believe there''s a God. Because I sure as hell know there''s a devil.', 21, 0), (240953, 'Despite everything, I believe people are really good at heart.', 986, 0), (240954, 'There''s not a woman in the world who won''t buy a Lie she wants to Believe', 42312, 0), (240955, 'Hans Selye, the pioneer in the understanding of human stress, was often asked the following question: "What is the most stressful condition a person can face?" His unexpected response: "Not having something to BELIEVE in.', 13515, 0), (240956, 'Though I adore the idea of Santa Claus, the Easter Bunny, Sandman, the Tooth Fairy, and such luminary characters—especially their altruism and devotion—I still don''t believe in them.  For I know the truth.  Only one such miracle worker exists who performs magic in my life, seeing to my wants and needs without fail.  That queen is my mother.  With unwavering faith I believe in her.', 1456, 0), (240957, 'Running my fastest not from my past. Running from those who have hurt me in it. And, they can''t catch me anymore. I escaped from the land of make believe.', 11722, 0), (240958, 'Life can be as easy as you wish to make it, or as difficult as you are prepared to believe that it is.', 11173, 0), (240959, 'I don''t know when I''ll able to knock in the door of her mind. But I believe in my love, enthusiasm and passion. Someday dream may come true.', 30375, 0), (240960, 'The secret to discovery is to never believe existing facts.', 7223, 0), (240961, 'Truth to tell, I''m right proud of Glory. She''s standing up for what she believes is right. All of us should lead our children to do that, don''t you know?', 42313, 0), (240962, 'If you''re still believing, then you''re almost there!', 3341, 0), (240963, 'If somebody says to you the quote"don''t judge the book by its cover", then better first close your eyes for a moment and try not to judge anybody at all. Even much better if you don''t have to believe in 100% with that quote.', 1296, 0), (240964, 'We keep hoping in God while reality keeps knocking at our door.', 42314, 0), (240965, 'It''s only a moment if you believe.', 42315, 0), (240966, 'But what I do believe is that if you''re a girl who was born in Homsea, a girl who lives in a nothing kind of house with an ordinary kind of family, then you can''t know everything about the world and that it''s probably good to keep an open mind about things, just in case.', 42316, 0), (240967, 'Believe in your dreams even when they seem lost', 1029, 0), (240968, 'Keep working. Keep trying. Keep believing. You still might not make it, but at least you gave it your best shot. If you don’t have calluses on your soul, this isn’t for you. Take up knitting instead.', 1840, 0), (240969, 'If you don''t believe in yourself, why should anyone else?', 9942, 0), (240970, 'Never underestimate what you can accomplish when you believe in yourself. (Unknown)', 41723, 0), (240971, 'The more we do to you,the less you seem to believe we are doing it.', 42317, 0), (240972, 'Of course I do, Jack! You have to beLIEve me!', 13237, 0), (240973, 'Take caution of what lies, in what you may beLIEve.', 3341, 0), (240974, '... I don''t believe in ghosts - not the scary white sheet, boogie-woogie type of ghost anyway. And yet ... I don''t disbelieve either. I''m kind of sitting on the ghost fence, dangling my legs on both sides, not sure which way to jump. I think I might be here for a while.', 42316, 0), (240975, 'Your visions will become clear only when you can look into your own heart. Who looks outside, dreams; who looks inside, awakes.', 472, 0), (240976, 'But you can''t get away from yourself. You can''t decide not to see yourself anymore. You can''t decide to turn off the noise in your head.', 212, 0), (240977, 'To say "I love you" one must know first how to say the "I".', 631, 0), (240978, 'I think....